{"tid":971303,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【港產獨角獸】WeLab上市申請失效","createTime":"2019-01-06T13:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-07T14:21:29.000Z","uid":65346,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5b6edecb05a559242feb685012097ed76669e16f","tid":971303,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T13:54:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190106/59111802\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190106%2F59111802&d=Yn22%2BRciTYZw5tTnbpOTrzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=96760567\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190106%2F59111802&h=523e414f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190106/59111802</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n港產獨角獸、網貸平台WeLab上市申請失效。根據港交所網站披露，WeLab上市申請現已處於失效狀態。公司發言人不予置評。<br />\nWeLab於去年7月3日向港交所提交IPO招股書，惟由於申請已失效，所有先前上載的招股文件內容均不能被閱取。<br />\n翻查媒體報道，WeLab 2017年總收入按年增逾4倍，達1.55億美元，當中大部份是來自內地貸款撮合服務收入以及信貸服務收入，分別為6,647萬美元5,824萬美元。全年扭虧為盈，賺1769萬美元，相當於接近14億港元。<br />\n事實上，去年底已傳出WeLab因目前市況波動及政策不明朗等因素，決定延遲其5億美元（約39億元）在港的上市計劃。上月28日，彭博引述消息報道，WeLab已要求銀行暫停上市籌備工作，現時尚無恢復上市工作的時間表，或轉為考慮尋求新一輪私募融資等方案。<br />\n根據集團網站介紹，WeLab旗下平台包括內地流動借貸平台「我來貸」、香港線上借貸平台WeLend，以及印尼的金融科技合資公司AWDA。"},{"pid":"f462b7d563cb287cd00d66a82bda5279ce6cfbb3","tid":971303,"uid":92512,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:29:13.000Z","msg":"抵撚死，呢間公司正垃圾"},{"pid":"a7b50aaadce77dcd590a788aa48e4a9d2def7d83","tid":971303,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"